et="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/Ho%E1%BA%A1-Xu%C3%A2n-%C4%90%C3%A0i-t%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-groI3PLDHmo7eeESIJSeJA">Hoạ Xuân Đài tức cảnh thi kỳ 1 - 和春臺即景詩其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/author-IGETeQBwf_c0CasyF8dTBQ">Trần Đình Tân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Hu%E1%BB%B3nh-Th%C3%BAc-Kh%C3%A1ng/Nh%C3%A2m-Ng%E1%BB%8D-nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%91%C3%A1n/poem-c1F-Ad1dv3Uf-Wgn9XZmqA">Nhâm Ngọ nguyên đán - 壬午元旦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Hu%E1%BB%B3nh-Th%C3%BAc-Kh%C3%A1ng/author-tWIJ_JcBg9FILAgkriOf3g">Huỳnh Thúc Kháng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-B%C3%B9i-H%E1%BB%AFu-Th%E1%BB%A9-Du-Thu%E1%BA%ADn-An-k%E1%BB%B3-3-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-t%E1%BA%A5n-th%E1%BA%A7n-ti%E1%BB%85n-kh%C3%A1ch/poem-9Y1mZDdmQLyHbVMQX9yaRw">Phụng hoạ Bùi Hữu Thứ “Du Thuận An” kỳ 3 - Đại tấn thần tiễn khách - 奉和裴有庶遊順安其三－代汛神餞客</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/author-IGETeQBwf_c0CasyF8dTBQ">Trần Đình Tân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1c/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-s%E1%BB%A9-%C4%91%C4%83ng-tr%C3%ACnh-t%E1%BB%B1-thu%E1%BA%ADt/poem-Jbo4CE9Vim98vO5_8l--SA">Phụng sứ đăng trình tự thuật - 奉使登程自述</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-KlUCS3ER6VvH2W9Ma4g25A">Nguyễn Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-C%E1%BA%A3nh-Minh/Tu%E1%BA%BF-%C3%A1n-h%C3%A0nh/poem-wAMQh2wG8MGNp6g7055UZw">Tuế án hành - 歲晏行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-C%E1%BA%A3nh-Minh/author-wg6EAaIQ8OL-TAAIuNs-Kg">Hà Cảnh Minh</a>)<br></div>	</div>
